Very good quality and quantity of food serving here.  Specialty selection could  have been provided with attractive prices.  A fantastic restaurant with superb feeling and savoury of enjoying food and beer.
Great food with great price... The only set back is that it was very pack on the day and food serve was kinda slow...

Delicious dinner for our final night in Hong Kong! The most incredible crab, and fried squid in delicious spices (which we just ate as a topping for the rice after!). One of the best meals I’ve had in HK. Super local spot.
Excellent taste !! I really love it!!

result.name: 金豪肥牛豬骨煲避風塘小炒

reviews.text: 有水準👍
執到錢都唔好去呀又逼又窄又冇招呼嗰啲所謂招牌菜不知所謂嗰個雞煲翅味精又重

金豪肥牛豬骨煲的餐廳位於深水埗青山道17號地下。主要菜式包括好味醬烤骨, 芥末牛柳粒, 避風塘炒蟹, 避風塘瀨尿蝦, 避風塘瀨尿蝦肉, 芥辣牛柳粒, 椒鹽鮮魷, 避風塘尿蝦肉, 龍 ...叫左個海鮮孖寶，四百幾蚊有四隻蟶子同一隻避風塘炒蟹，蟶子皇長過我手掌，肉又肥，又爽口 ...但對除海鮮殼...深水埗地膽的他，毫不猶疑推薦我們試試避風塘 椒鹽瀨尿蝦肉不用除殼、又有養顏雞湯翅... 食評相片. 打邊爐好地方.
今日上菜特別快，樓面趕客重快。食左40分鐘，放低筷子，成柸酒都未飲，成枱執清
Good value and nice foods. suitable for big group of people as the portion is quite huge. Reservation is recommended
